<answer fraction="100" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
By the usual significance level <span class="math inline">\(\alpha\)</span> = 5% to reduce to <span class="math inline">\(\alpha\)</span> = 1%.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
Due to the usual significance level <span class="math inline">\(\alpha\)</span> = 5% to increase to <span class="math inline">\(\alpha\)</span> = 10%.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
<answer fraction="0" format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
By choosing a 99% confidence interval.
</p>]]></text>
</answer>
